    "Articles would often raise general, superficial concerns regarding the misuse of AI in the introduction or conclusion of a given article without examining and scrutinizing the topic in detail.",
    "(26) (22) While AI has also been covered in a effectual, pragmatic way, particularly when covering the applications of AI in finance and healthcare (25), one could argue that the more dramatic headlines frequently overshadow these articles.",
